  <documentation>
  		<p>
      		The job reads an email incoming box and provides some actions for each email found.<br/> 
      		The actions to be executed with the emails is defined in the <paramref>mail_action</paramref> parameter.<br/> 
      		All general "mail.*", POP3 "mail.pop3.*" and IMAP "mail.imap.*" properties for Java Mail can be used for the connection to the mail server. See here for
      		<ul>
      			<li><a href="https://javaee.github.io/javamail/docs/api/javax/mail/package-summary.html">general mail properties</a></li>
      			<li><a href="https://javaee.github.io/javamail/docs/api/com/sun/mail/pop3/package-summary.html">POP3 mail properties</a></li>
      			<li><a href="https://javaee.github.io/javamail/docs/api/com/sun/mail/imap/package-summary.html">IMAP mail properties</a></li>
      		</ul> 
